              <p class="text-sm text-gray-400 mt-2">Final load time</p>
              <p class="text-xs text-gray-500">from 4.2s</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#10B981] font-black">Day 1-30:</span>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Google recrawled site. Noticed speed improvement. Re-indexed pages.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#10B981] font-black">Day 31-60:</span>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Rankings climbed steadily. User engagement metrics improved.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <span class="text-[#10B981] font-black">Day 61-90:</span>
            <p class="text-gray-700">Stabilized in top positions. Traffic consistently higher. Client: "Why didn't agency do this?"</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- TOP PICKS -->
  <section class="py-16 bg-white">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
