            <p class="text-[#10B981] font-black uppercase tracking-wider text-sm mt-1">Best for: Hands-off SEO automation</p>
          </div>
          <div class="text-4xl font-black text-[#10B981]">9.0/10</div>
        </div>

        <div class="space-y-4 mb-6">
          <p class="text-gray-900 font-black text-lg">Why Mixo wins for SEO:</p>
          <ul class="text-gray-700 space-y-2">
